org.productivity.java.habitat4j.common
Class AbstractServerIdentityManager

java.lang.Object
  org.productivity.java.habitat4j.common.AbstractServerIdentityManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
Habitat4JConstants
Direct Known Subclasses:
ServerIdentityManager
public abstract class AbstractServerIdentityManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements Habitat4JConstants

ServerIdentityManager provides access to a server-wide XML file called an "identity" file. This class manages the system-wide instance of ServerIdentity, which provides the PropertyListManager with information used to load properties based on the appropriate context.
